        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段偏軟 恒指跌115點報24115點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段向下，恒生指數開市報24115點，跌115點或0.48%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報6016點，跌21點或0.35%；國企指數以8873點開市，跌40點或0.45%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">多家公司於上周五收市後及周末發盈警，股價今早於競價時段亦普遍受壓。龍湖(00960)開報10.8元，跌1.1%；越秀地產(00123)開報5.53元，跌1.6%。上周曾炒上的奈雪的茶(02150)，今早開報1.5元，跌8.54%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">相反，太興集團(06811)雖然為2024年度業績發盈警，但表明去年下半年業績有改善，按年及較去年上半年均有增長；該股今早開報0.83元，升2.47%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：太興Facebook\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/592x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230814_FI_source-web_太興-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：太興Facebook\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/592x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230814_FI_source-web_太興-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：太興Facebook</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒大物業(06666)預期去年盈利倒退的同時，表明財務狀況持續改善；該股今早開報0.78元，也升1.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，金朝陽(00878)獲大股東以每股8.5元提私有化；該股今早復牌應聲彈升，開報7.69元；升39.82%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14764491-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c115%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b124115%e9%bb%9e",
